Last week, average concentrations were reported in and around the Pinellas district, from low to high concentrations in the Hillsborough coastal zone, high concentrations in Manati and Sarasota and coastal areas, average concentrations in Charlotte County, high concentrations on the Li District coast, and low concentrations in Collier District.
